<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$liu-ban-xian" href="/people/liu-ban-xian">刘半仙</a>，<strong title="苦逼科研民工~" class="zu-question-my-bio">苦逼科研民工~</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="8">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$zhang-gun-kai" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/zhang-gun-kai" class="zg-link" title="呆萌未知子">呆萌未知子</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yue-li-72" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yue-li-72" class="zg-link" title="月鲤">月鲤</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="394114" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">作为一枚在读博士，LZ我告诉你：<br><br><br><b>如果一个博士招人喜欢，那么他/她不读博士也（hui）同（geng）样（jia）招人喜欢。</b><br><br><br>招不招人喜欢跟读不读博士真的没多少关系，而且一般情况下读了博士的话在受欢迎程度上还会减分，女博尤甚。。。（不是我对女博士有偏见啊，相反，我对女博一点偏见都没有~我只是陈述一种较普遍的社会观点）
<a href="/question/20534096/answer/19159405" class="toggle-expand">显示全部</a>
<div class="fixed-summary-mask"></div>
</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
